Author: hunnyangel
Text: Something that helped my gf and I was realizing that we can’t control what the other one does. Her and I both urge each other towards habits that cause less damage but still feel safe, but in the end make sure we both know that we can’t control the way the other one eats.  Idk if that would work for your specific situation, cause idk what goes on behind the scenes, but this is just something that semi-works for her and I.
